Description.description: UNPARALLELED EXPERTISE FOR CRM PORTALS FOR DYNAMICS 365 Adoxio is known around the globe in the Dynamics communities for our expertly-configured Portal solutions integrated directly into Microsoft Dynamics 365. Adoxio's Portal solutions transform Microsoft Dynamics 365 into a powerful web engagement platform, enabling organizations to: • Give stakeholders secure access to read and write data through their PC, laptop, tablet, and mobile device browsers • Deliver sophisticated, web-enabled applications with comprehensive back-office Microsoft Dynamics 365 integration • Provide robust security for local, federated, and active directory as well as two-factor authentication • Build and manage entire communities across internet, intranet and extranet networks with CRM Portal's extensive profile management and self-service features • Data captured via your Portal is instantly available within your Dynamics 365 platform and can be used to trigger workflows, activities, and customize your visitor’s view of information dynamically in real-time - perfect for reporting and self-service applications
